File":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260421174123"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260421180059","id":"zettel.20260421180059","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260421174751","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":3,"offset":1582},"end":{"line":38,"column":28,"offset":1607},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260421174751"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":150,"column":3,"offset":13910},"end":{"line":150,"column":28,"offset":13935},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421180059"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260421184439","id":"zettel.20260421184439","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":3,"offset":2178},"end":{"line":48,"column":28,"offset":2203},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421180059"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260421193757","id":"zettel.20260421193757","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":65,"column":3,"offset":2054},"end":{"line":65,"column":28,"offset":2079},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421180059"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.ai-native","id":"zettel.moc.ai-native","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":54,"column":3,"offset":4645},"end":{"line":54,"column":28,"offset":4670},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421180059"}],"anchors":{"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka":{"type":"header","text":"Pertanyaan yang dibuka","value":"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka","line":17,"column":0,"depth":2},"klaim-utama":{"type":"header","text":"Klaim utama","value":"klaim-utama","line":23,"column":0,"depth":2},"penjelasan":{"type":"header","text":"Penjelasan","value":"penjelasan","line":29,"column":0,"depth":2},"implikasi":{"type":"header","text":"Implikasi","value":"implikasi","line":43,"column":0,"depth":2},"lihat-juga":{"type":"header","text":"Lihat juga","value":"lihat-juga","line":49,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"checkpoint-preview-membuat-review-manusia-fokus-pada-pemahaman-bukan-sekadar-diff\">Checkpoint Preview membuat review manusia fokus pada pemahaman, bukan sekadar diff<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#checkpoint-preview-membuat-review-manusia-fokus-pada-pemahaman-bukan-sekadar-diff\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\">Pertanyaan yang dibuka<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Mengapa git diff saja tidak cukup untuk review perubahan AI-native?</li>\n<li>Bagaimana Checkpoint Preview membantu reviewer membangun model mental perubahan?</li>\n<li>Apa perbedaan antara review sebagai bug hunt dan review sebagai comprehension workflow?</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"klaim-utama\">Klaim utama<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#klaim-utama\"></a></h2>\n<p>Checkpoint Preview bukan alat bug hunt otomatis. Ia adalah workflow review interaktif yang menyusun ulang perubahan agar manusia bisa memahami intent dan desain sebelum mengambil keputusan.</p>\n<p>Review ini penting karena diff tradisional mempresentasikan perubahan berdasarkan file order, bukan berdasarkan cara manusia membangun pemahaman.</p>\n<h2 id=\"penjelasan\">Penjelasan<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#penjelasan\"></a></h2>\n<p>Dalam BMAD, Quick Dev mengurangi interupsi manusia saat implementasi. Checkpoint Preview membawa manusia kembali ke loop saat keputusan akhir diperlukan.</p>\n<p>Checkpoint Preview mendorong reviewer untuk memulai dari:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>orientasi scope dan surface area,</li>\n<li>walkthrough berdasarkan concern,</li>\n<li>detail pass pada risiko tinggi,</li>\n<li>observasi perilaku melalui testing,</li>\n<li>wrap-up keputusan.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ini membuat review lebih seperti membentuk model mental daripada membaca daftar perubahan.</p>\n<h2 id=\"implikasi\">Implikasi<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#implikasi\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Reviewer tidak lagi bergantung pada urutan file atau hunk di git diff.</li>\n<li>Attention manusia dialokasikan ke area blast radius tinggi, bukan semua perubahan sekaligus.</li>\n<li>Review menjadi activity of judgment, bukan activity of reconstruction.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"lihat-juga\">Lihat juga<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#lihat-juga\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">zettel.literature.checkpoint-preview (Private)</a> — literature note BMAD Checkpoint Preview</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421174123\">BMAD Quick Dev mengoptimalkan attention manusia, bukan sekadar kecepatan model</a> — BMAD Quick Dev mengoptimalkan attention manusia, bukan sekadar kecepatan model</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421174751\">Quick Dev diagram: node-by-node diagnosis layer dan alur koreksi</a> — Quick Dev diagram: node-by-node diagnosis layer dan alur koreksi</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">bmad (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">checkpoint-preview (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">review (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">ai-native (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421184439\">Adversarial Review memaksa reviewer beralih dari rasa aman ke pencarian kelemahan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421193757\">Kapan struktur AI-native jadi layak dipakai dan kapan ia justru overkill</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.ai-native\">MOC AI-native engineering</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"